♫Tearing through the night♫

248
00:12:16,230 --> 00:12:19,940
♫Suddenly taking the lead, secretly stealing♫

249
00:12:20,750 --> 00:12:26,280
♫Beneath the feather fan, people's hearts are dark, fading away in smoke♫

250
00:12:27,030 --> 00:12:32,290
♫How is fate rewritten?♫

251
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:32,580
Wear a phoenix crown.

252
00:12:42,910 --> 00:12:44,430
Then I want Xu Hanzhi

253
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:46,170
to crown me personally

254
00:12:46,370 --> 00:12:48,170
and swear allegiance.

255
00:12:49,370 --> 00:12:50,570
If he refuses,

256
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,240
I will kill him with my own hands.

257
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:55,620
Indeed.

258
00:12:56,090 --> 00:12:58,010
Once people have power,

259
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:00,020
they will certainly obtain

260
00:13:00,050 --> 00:13:01,930
what they desire.

